#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/grpc-service-consumption.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A gRPC client interceptor can be implemented by a CDI bean that also implements the `io.grpc.ClientInterceptor` interface.\n"
